<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="success-n">success <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /sək'ses/    美 /sək'ses/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 成功；成就：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>achieve / earn / win great success in life
在人生中取得巨大的成就</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had suggested his doing it another way, but <strong>without success</strong>.  
我建议他用别的方式做，但他没听。</p><footer>2011 四川</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Always bear in mind that your own resolution to success is more important than any one thing.
永远记住：成功的决心比任何一件事都重要。</p><footer>——林肯</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] 成功的人 / 事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is <strong>a great success</strong> as a writer. 
作为作家他很成功。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A true friend is one who overlooks your failures and tolerates your successes.
真正的朋友从不追究你的过错，也从不妒忌你的成功。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It is important to remember that success <strong><em>_</em></strong> (be) a sum of small efforts made each day and often <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (take) years to achieve.   （2015 湖南改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. is; takes  </p></div>